could mean many things...Roberts might know...a hidden message...left behind...fluttering heart...maybe fear...or love...a secret passage...someone escaped...a convict perhaps...you felt that?
Yeah, so is that who's up there in the attic, is it a human spirit or is it a spirit that's never been born?
possibly...burning candle...never born...Adrian...empty hallway...rustling leaves...guilty...whispered secret...
Okay, so... Angie, who do you know to love Mayor Roberts? Or Adrienne?
Adrienne...bitter tears...Mayor Roberts...Valerie...distant echo...abandoned house...fluttering heart...confession...
warm hug...hidden door...shattered dreams...Jackson...forgive...forgotten melody...redemption...weathered smile...maybe...

something was lost...a heart never healed...a story left untold...testimony never heard...aching heart still waits...unfinished business clings...a witness holds the key...maybe it needs you to see it...to speak it...to free it...do you feel it?
